criteria.driver_alignment:
Discover — established the 10-year operating horizon as a defining project parameter;  
Represent — translated the horizon into a year-by-year incremental cash flow model;  
Implement/Validate — implemented year0–year10 cash flows, terminal value and working capital recovery, and checked payback metrics against the 10-year life;  
Evolve — discussed implications for forecasting (noting risks after year five).
